--> Linux Line "rw shingle initrd=/install/initrd.gz init=bin/bash" + FIO ... 

--> root passwd __ ___ -> "exec /sbin/init" . Done 

-------------------------------Identify the user by sign------------------------------------------------------------------- 

root@user:~# | this the root user . 

user@:~$ | non-root user.

#terminal zoom in => clt+shift and_press '='
